// Chart data for revenue trends const revenueData = [ { month: "January", revenue: 18600, bookings: 80 }, { month: "February", revenue: 30500, bookings: 120 }, { month: "March", revenue: 23700, bookings: 95 }, { month: "April", revenue: 17300, bookings: 70 }, { month: "May", revenue: 20900, bookings: 85 }, { month: "June", revenue: 21400, bookings: 90 }, ]; const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false); useEffect(() => { if (isAdmin) { fetchDashboardStats(); } }, [isAdmin]); const fetchDashboardStats = async () => { try { const response = await axios.get('/api/reports/dashboard'); setStats(prev => ({ ...prev, ...response.data })); } catch (error) { console.error('Error fetching dashboard stats:', error); } }; const adminHeaderStats = [ { label: 'Total Cars', value: stats.totalCars, icon: BoxIcon }, { label: 'Total Bookings', value: stats.totalBookings, icon: CalendarIcon }, { label: 'Overdue Rentals', value: stats.overdueRentals, icon: CalendarIcon }, { label: 'Active Users', value: stats.activeUsers, icon: BoxIcon } ];
